      • RESET_SLOW_WRITES

        public static final BooleanConfOption RESET_SLOW_WRITES
        Whether or not we should track the write speed, and try writing to a new file if write operations get too slow. Default is not resetting slow writes.

      • WRITE_RESET_TIMEOUT

        public static final LongConfOption WRITE_RESET_TIMEOUT
        If resetting slow writes is used, how long should a write take in order for a new file to be created. Default is 10s as threshold for slow writes.
